441,0005-001115-0002882-0009,"[""girls"",""jackets-and-coats"",""parkas-and-puffer-jackets""]","The winter chills are no match for this long puffer anorak. Shown in silver, it boasts a cozy fleece lining, snap and zip pockets and a faux fur trimmed hood with snap button closures.
